From fully funding our elections to protecting voters on the margins, this package is about safeguarding democracy at every level.

60 years after the Voting Rights Act, we must finish the work. That means tearing down barriers and building a system that works for everyone.

No American should be denied their right to vote, not because of where they live, how much they make, or their housing status.
